import "../UploadVideoForm/UploadVideoForm.scss";

function UploadVideoForm() {
  return (
    <uploadvideoform className="comment-form">
      <form className="comment__form">
        <label for="comment" className="comment__header">
          TITLE YOUR VIDEO
          <input
            type="text"
            className="comment__input"
            id="comment"
            name="comment"
            placeholder="Add a title to your video"
          ></input>
        </label>
        <label for="comment" className="comment__header">
          ADD A VIDEO DESCRIPTION
          <input
            type="text"
            className="comment__input"
            id="comment"
            name="comment"
            placeholder="Add a description to your video"
          ></input>
        </label>
        <button className="comment__btn">PUBLISH</button>
        <button className="comment__btn">CANCEL</button>
      </form>
    </uploadvideoform>
  );
}

export default UploadVideoForm;
